{"tid":1635341,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS和你CALL","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T10:23:58.000Z","uid":1089,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"27087ce6ed49e821b09e06402d2e3419b8aa0157","tid":1635341,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"用iPhone iPad既你<br />\n800-908-988，同我CALL爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度都有好多個POST講過iOS13.0 emoji輸入法國旗list係有中華民國國旗，但係iOS 13.1.1就消失左<br />\n<br />\n我分別用一部iOS13.0 iPhone Xs同埋13.1.1 iPad mini做例子打上Apple Support質問<br />\n開頭夠膽死同我講政治問題不討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻駁返佢唔係政治問題，係用戶體驗問題<br />\n有咩理由因為係香港地區就要比其他地區少一個emoji用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後先肯記錄在案，跟住仲要同我講其實好多人反映呢個問題<br />\n我就等佢點覆，3日內冇答覆繼續用個caseID質鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a54f9a7abf55ffd65cd63253b1d8e001f1b68","tid":1635341,"uid":1089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"中華民國國旗係呢支🇹🇼<br />\n唔係呢支🇼🇸<br />\n<br />\n如果你部機個emoji list仲有呢支旗，只有兩個可能性<br />\n一係你部機版本仲係iOS13.0或以下<br />\n一係就地區SET左唔係香港/Hong Kong SAR"},{"pid":"100392ae16200708ea7ec8e2f8ba34fffe54880b","tid":1635341,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"蘋果店 太沉悶？"},{"pid":"01c56bd8ae1a30eb6546869b9f787b53b7e6a8c7","tid":1635341,"uid":1089,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"100392ae16200708ea7ec8e2f8ba34fffe54880b","tid":1635341,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"蘋果店 太沉悶？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"咪亂去／亂叫人去裝修呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係用戶體驗問題，唔係政治問題"},{"pid":"414a38d3c0cd96a5d69591806108236cd440eaf1","tid":1635341,"uid":191385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c